      <title>L2 Point 创始人谈首支基金和投资策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-25/l2-point-founder-on-inaugural-fund-investment-strategy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[L2 Point Management 最近关闭了其首只基金，资本接近 4.6 亿美元。管理合伙人、创始人兼首席信息官 Kerstin Dittmar 讨论了增长资本的结构以及进军私募股权。她在“彭博市场”节目中与 Sonali Basak 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-25/l2-point-founder-on-inaugural-fund-investment-strategy-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 19:59:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
